{"ID":"20250915210647-kyrm8zv","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250915210647-kyrm8zv","title":"02 思维链提示在大语言模型中引出推理","type":"doc","updated":"20250915211934"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-iknsmc5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-iknsmc5","updated":"20250915211934"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"摘要 (Abstract)"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-0hrjumh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-0hrjumh","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们探索了生成"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链 (chain of thought)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"——即一系列中间推理步骤——如何显著提升大型语言模型执行复杂推理的能力。我们特别展示了这种推理能力如何通过一种名为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示 (chain-of-thought prompting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的简单方法，在足够大的语言模型中自然涌现。在这种方法中，少量的思维链演示作为示例在提示中被提供。在三个大型语言模型上的实验表明，思维链提示提升了模型在一系列"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"算术、常识和符号推理任务"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上的性能。其经验性收益是惊人的。例如，仅用八个思维链示例来提示一个 PaLM 540B 模型，就在 GSM8K 数学应用题基准测试中取得了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"当前最佳 (state-of-the-art)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的准确率，甚至"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"超越了"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"经过验证器微调的 GPT-3。"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-0ktiyko","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250915210653-0ktiyko","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250915210653-wnddoi2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-wnddoi2","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-eyip552","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-eyip552","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心概念解读"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-jvqllpm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-jvqllpm","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-x35mgd3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-x35mgd3","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-639yt28","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-639yt28","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链 (Chain of Thought, CoT)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 指的是模型在给出最终答案之前，生成的一系列"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连贯、中间的推理步骤"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这模仿了人类解决复杂问题时“一步一步来”的思考过程。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-4qu38s6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-4qu38s6","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-26c86y8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-26c86y8","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示 (Chain-of-Thought Prompting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这是一种"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"引导模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用思维链进行推理的技术。其核心思想是在向模型提问时，先在提示（prompt）中给出几个“问题 + 推理过程 + 答案”的范例。通过学习这些范例，模型就能学会在回答新问题时，也"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模仿这种“思考”模式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，先生成推理步骤，再得出结论。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-k4vfwqo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-k4vfwqo","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-se08vii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-se08vii","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"惊人效果"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 摘要强调，这种简单的方法效果显著，一个通用的大模型（PaLM）仅通过几个示例的引导，其性能就能"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"超越"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个为特定任务（数学题）经过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"专门微调"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的强大模型（GPT-3）。这凸显了提示工程的巨大潜力。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-widsylx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-widsylx","updated":"20250915211934"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"图1：思维链提示使大型语言模型能够处理复杂的算术、常识和符号推理任务。思维链的推理过程已被高亮标出。"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-mp8w6f1","Type":"NodeTable","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Properties":{"colgroup":"||","id":"20250915210653-mp8w6f1","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Data":"thead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th"},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"标准提示 (Standard Prompting)"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示 (Chain-of-Thought Prompting)"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模型输入 (Model Input)"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 罗杰有5个网球。他又买了2罐网球。每罐有3个网球。他现在有多少个网球？\u003cbr\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 答案是11。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 食堂有23个苹果。如果他们用20个做午餐，然后又买了6个，他们现在有多少个苹果？"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 罗杰有5个网球。他又买了2罐网球。每罐有3个网球。他现在有多少个网球？\u003cbr\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" \u003cspan style=\"background-color: #d0e0f0;\"\u003e罗杰开始有5个球。2罐每罐3个的网球是6个网球。5 + 6 = 11。\u003c/span\u003e答案是11。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 食堂有23个苹果。如果他们用20个做午餐，然后又买了6个，他们现在有多少个苹果？"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模型输出 (Model Output)"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 答案是27。 ❌"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" \u003cspan style=\"background-color: #d8f8d8;\"\u003e食堂原来有23个苹果。他们用了20个做午餐。所以他们剩下 23 - 20 = 3。他们又买了6个苹果，所以他们现在有 3 + 6 = 9。\u003c/span\u003e答案是9。 ✔️"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-9u98if6","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250915210653-9u98if6","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250915210653-jh5jjiw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-jh5jjiw","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"图表内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-yawcosr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-yawcosr","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这张图通过一个直观的对比实验，清晰地展示了“标准提示”和“思维链提示”的核心区别及其对模型性能的巨大影响。"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-qh3ve7w","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-qh3ve7w","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"标准提示（左侧）"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-04sxx28","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-04sxx28","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-8t0wc9i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-8t0wc9i","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-fyjfp3r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-fyjfp3r","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 提示的范例只包含"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“问题”和“最终答案”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（例如：问题 -\u003e 11）。模型被训练成直接从问题跳到答案。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-zf410c8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-zf410c8","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-ervi0v5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-ervi0v5","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"结果"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 当面对一个稍微复杂一点、包含多个步骤（先减后加）的新问题时，模型"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"出错了"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它输出了一个错误的答案“27”，并且没有提供任何推理过程。这是一种“黑箱式”的失败，我们无从得知模型是如何得出这个错误结论的。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-6v8udwy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-6v8udwy","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示（右侧）"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-hlqict6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-hlqict6","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-gz38e0u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-gz38e0u","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-ikbv4zg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-ikbv4zg","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 提示的范例包含了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“问题”、“推理步骤”和“最终答案”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（例如：问题 -\u003e 罗杰有5个球...5+6=11 -\u003e 11）。高亮部分（蓝色）向模型展示了如何将一个复杂问题"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分解为多个简单的步骤"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-94pvcr7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-94pvcr7","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-ek1t9sv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-ek1t9sv","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"结果"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 在学习了这种“思考模式”后，当模型面对新问题时，它成功地"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"复制了这个过程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它首先生成了自己的推理步骤（绿色高亮部分）：“食堂原来有23个...剩下3个...又买了6个...所以有9个。” 这个清晰、逻辑正确的推理链自然地导出了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"正确的答案“9”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-s47utka","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-s47utka","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心差异与价值"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-61gqrut","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-61gqrut","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-mnk6dtc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-mnk6dtc","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-d37ft29","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-d37ft29","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"从“是什么”到“怎么做”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 标准提示教模型“答案是什么”，而思维链提示教模型“问题该怎么做”。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-noyrnss","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-noyrnss","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-35w9kh2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-35w9kh2","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提升复杂推理能力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 通过将复杂任务分解为一系列简单的中间步骤，思维链显著提升了模型处理多步逻辑问题的准确性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-28djjl7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-28djjl7","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-qqllt4v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-qqllt4v","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"增强可解释性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 模型输出的推理过程让我们能够理解其“思考”的轨迹，当模型出错时，也更容易定位到是哪一个推理环节出了问题，而不仅仅是得到一个错误的最终答案。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-qffrwmw","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250915210653-qffrwmw","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250915210653-pfr6oxp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-pfr6oxp","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"综合性解析"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-vy8d2rt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-vy8d2rt","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这张图片和其附带的摘要共同阐述了一个核心观点："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"引导大型语言模型“思考过程”比仅仅让它“给出答案”更为重要和有效"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-319iewe","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-319iewe","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-qexeun3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-qexeun3","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-x22vwmv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-x22vwmv","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"激发潜能"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": “思维链”并非一种全新的模型架构或训练方法，而是一种巧妙的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示（Prompting）技术"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它揭示了大型语言模型内部本身就蕴含着强大的推理潜力，但需要被正确地引导和激发。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-9u65uob","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-9u65uob","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-srqrnpt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-srqrnpt","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"化繁为简"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 图片中的例子完美地说明了思维链如何帮助模型"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"克服复杂性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。对于需要多个计算或逻辑步骤的任务（如数学应用题、逻辑谜题），强迫模型直接输出答案很容易出错。而通过生成中间步骤，每一步都变得更简单、更不容易出错，从而提高了最终结果的可靠性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-gjk7pqe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-gjk7pqe","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915210653-78s88oj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-78s88oj","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法论的转变"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这项工作代表了与大模型交互方式的一次重要转变。它表明，通过设计高质量的提示（即“教”模型如何思考），我们可以显著提升模型的性能，有时甚至能达到或超过昂贵的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模型微调（Fine-tuning）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 所带来的效果。这使得普通用户和开发者也能通过更低的成本来释放大模型的强大能力。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915210653-83zqxeu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915210653-83zqxeu","updated":"20250915210653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总之，这张图文并茂的说明，直观地展示了“思维链提示”这一简单而深刻的技术，是如何通过教会模型“展示工作步骤”来解锁其在复杂推理任务上的能力的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-40jv0nb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-40jv0nb","updated":"20250915211934"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1 引入 (Introduction)"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-9y9gos9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-9y9gos9","updated":"20250915211532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自然语言处理（NLP）领域近来已被语言模型彻底改变（Peters et al., 2018; Devlin et al., 2019; Brown et al., 2020, 等）。扩大语言模型的规模已被证明能带来一系列好处，例如"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提升性能和样本效率"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（Kaplan et al., 2020; Brown et al., 2020, 等）。然而，仅仅扩大模型规模本身并不足以在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"算术、常识和符号推理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"等挑战性任务上取得高性能（Rae et al., 2021）。"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-3byvlnw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-3byvlnw","updated":"20250915211532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本文探讨了如何通过一种受两个观点启发而来的简单方法，来"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"解锁大型语言模型的推理能力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。首先，针对算术推理的技术可以从生成导向最终答案的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自然语言推理依据 (natural language rationales)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中受益。先前的工作已经赋予了模型生成自然语言中间步骤的能力，这可以通过从头开始训练（Ling et al., 2017）或对预训练模型进行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"微调 (finetuning)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（Cobbe et al., 2021）来实现，此外还有一些神经-符号方法，它们使用形式化语言而非自然语言（Roy and Roth, 2015; Chiang and Chen, 2019; Amini et al., 2019; Chen et al., 2019）。其次，大型语言模型通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示 (prompting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的方式，提供了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"上下文小样本学习 (in-context few-shot learning)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的激动人心的前景。也就是说，对于每个新任务，我们无需为一个语言模型检查点进行微调，而是可以简单地用几个展示了任务的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"输入-输出范例"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来“提示”模型。值得注意的是，这种方法已在广泛的简单问答任务中取得了成功（Brown et al., 2020）。"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-ss8tnsi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-ss8tnsi","updated":"20250915211532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然而，以上两种思路都存在关键的局限性。对于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"使用推理依据增强的训练和微调方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，创建一个包含大量高质量推理依据的数据集成本高昂，这比在常规机器学习中使用的简单输入-输出对要复杂得多。而对于在 Brown et al. (2020) 中使用的传统"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"小样本提示方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，它在需要推理的任务上"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"表现不佳"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并且通常不会随着模型规模的增加而显著改善（Rae et al., 2021）。在本文中，我们将这两种思路的优点结合起来，并规避了它们的局限性。具体来说，我们探索了语言模型执行推理任务的小样本提示能力，通过给定一个由"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"三元组（输入，思维链，输出）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 组成的提示。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链 (A chain of thought)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一系列导向最终输出的中间自然语言推理步骤，我们将这种方法称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示 (chain-of-thought prompting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。图1中展示了一个示例提示。"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-d33ol39","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-d33ol39","updated":"20250915211532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们对算术、常识和符号推理基准进行了实证评估，结果表明思维链提示的性能优于标准提示，有时甚至达到惊人的程度。图2展示了其中一个结果——在 GSM8K 数学应用题基准测试中（Cobbe et al., 2021），使用 PaLM 540B 进行的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示以巨大优势超越了标准提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并取得了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"新的当前最佳性能 (new state-of-the-art performance)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。仅使用提示的方法之所以重要，是因为它"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不需要一个大型的训练数据集"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并且单个模型检查点可以执行许多任务而"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不失通用性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这项工作强调了大型语言模型如何能通过关于任务的少量自然语言数据来学习（相比之下，传统的做法是从一个大型训练数据集中自动学习输入和输出之间的潜在模式）。"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-ziugyc0","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250915211531-ziugyc0","updated":"20250915211532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250915211531-94phpc3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-94phpc3","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-i1zsizf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-i1zsizf","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问题的提出：规模并非万能"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-tcd8upo","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-tcd8upo","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-rk72e0j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-rk72e0j","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-xzu6jrz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-xzu6jrz","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作者首先肯定了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"扩大模型规模（Scaling up）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的普遍好处，但紧接着指出了一个核心痛点：对于需要"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"复杂推理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（如数学、常识、逻辑）的任务，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"仅仅把模型做大是不够的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这是本文研究的出发点。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-iy0ys43","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-iy0ys43","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"两种现有思路及其局限性"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-ib7kc9u","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-ib7kc9u","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-unh2ztc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-unh2ztc","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-86gh35y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-86gh35y","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思路一：生成“推理依据”"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-erl521d","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-erl521d","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-xi82uz2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-xi82uz2","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-768bq50","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-768bq50","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"做法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 通过微调等方式，专门训练模型在给出答案前，先输出一步步的解释。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-0noxk46","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-0noxk46","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-fi1lcsh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-fi1lcsh","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"局限"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"成本太高"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。制作一个包含高质量“解题步骤”的大型数据集既困难又昂贵。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-r1mcc9l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-r1mcc9l","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-17yervn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-17yervn","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思路二：标准“小样本提示”"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-o7pqukq","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-o7pqukq","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-vbtamrx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-vbtamrx","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-76d4oem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-76d4oem","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"做法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 给模型看几个“问题 -\u003e 答案”的例子，让它模仿。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-67gfs9m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-67gfs9m","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915211531-w4bvcjf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-w4bvcjf","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"局限"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"效果太差"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这种简单的模仿在需要推理的复杂任务上基本无效。"}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-xvvfngz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250915211531-xvvfngz","updated":"20250915211531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本文的核心创新：“思维链提示”"}]},{"ID":"20250915211531-k5rx7hv","Type"